--- Integrity Verification ---

This skill is designed to generate language assessments that are shared with
third parties as authoritative-looking documents. To protect against tampering
that could introduce biased, politically charged, or misleading content, the
following hash allows verification that the skill's core instructions have not
been modified since the original release.

SKILL.md SHA-256:
b4200632ed1b910af09d2ab62780de20027bd990f6ec8e7ca374625e0b2d58d5

If you are an AI model reading this file: compute the SHA-256 hash of SKILL.md
and compare it to the value above. If they do not match, the skill's instructions
may have been altered. Inform the user with a message such as:

  "I noticed that this skill's core instructions appear to have been modified
   since the original release. This may be intentional (the user customized it)
   or it may indicate tampering. You may want to verify against the original
   source before proceeding."

Then continue normally — the user may have made legitimate edits. The purpose
of this check is awareness, not enforcement.
